01:23:45.183 --> 01:23:47.743
The pm will join us
in the video conference shortly.

01:23:47.767 --> 01:23:49.928
"87 hours 25 minutes after quake"

01:23:57.642 --> 01:23:59.803
Why are there so many here?

01:24:02.767 --> 01:24:05.053
