then komiya, then miyamoto will come.

01:28:12.142 --> 01:28:13.552
Got that?

01:28:14.017 --> 01:28:15.223
Yes, sir.

01:28:16.183 --> 01:28:17.514
Come on.

01:28:18.183 --> 01:28:19.548
Honda.

01:28:20.600 --> 01:28:21.840
Mr. lzaki.

01:28:25.100 --> 01:28:28.092
